\frametitle{Solution by tracing back on characteristics}

The general solution for acoustics:
\[
\begin{split}
q(x,t) &= w^1(x-\lambda^1t,0)r^1 + w^2(x-\lambda^2 t,0)r^2\\
& = w^1(x+c_0t,0)r^1 + w^2(x-c_0t,0)r^2
\end{split} 
\]

